Comment: 10,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.56,0:00:21.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Are you all doing okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.06,0:00:25.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Hold on, Todoggler! Calm down...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:28.06,0:00:29.81,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:29.81,0:00:31.27,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,You good?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.27,0:00:33.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’m... all... good...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:41.10,0:00:43.06,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Huh? The ship’s being suspended?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:43.48,0:00:46.52,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Yes. I’m afraid a member of the crew \N is quitting next week,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:46.52,0:00:49.06,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,and they just can’t \N make it work without them.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:50.73,0:00:54.35,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Sounds like they’re way overdue \N for some new staff.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:54.35,0:00:56.56,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,We’re short-handed \N over here, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:56.56,0:00:58.31,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,You have a point...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.10,0:01:01.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Um, have you seen Todoggler?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:01.52,0:01:02.81,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:02.81,0:01:04.06,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.06,0:01:05.90,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.56,0:01:08.90,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Now there’s a lively one!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.56,0:01:12.56,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Haru! Alisa! \N Can I get a little help?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:12.56,0:01:13.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:13.19,0:01:14.48,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Yeah, coming...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:16.65,0:01:19.90,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:25.94,0:01:29.06,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Go! Yanappe, Baoppe, Hiyappe!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:38.06,0:01:39.44,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.90,0:01:47.90,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Todoggler! Stop!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.15,0:01:52.40,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,All right! Good!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:56.02,0:01:59.90,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Sorry my Todoggler \N is causing you so much trouble.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.90,0:02:03.06,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Man, you’re a lifesaver, Uncle Dan!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.06,0:02:04.73,Main,Haru & Alisa,0,0,0,,“Uncle”?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.48,0:02:16.98,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,He used to look after me \N when I was only like, {\i1}this{\i0} big!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:16.98,0:02:20.48,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Uncle’d let us on his boat \N all the time!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.06,0:02:22.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Boat?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.48,0:02:25.06,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I was a fisherman \N until fairly recently.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.06,0:02:26.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.52,0:02:29.81,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Uncle used to be \N {\i1}this{\i0} macho back then!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.81,0:02:32.06,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,He was real scary!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.06,0:02:35.27,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,And if I ever played pranks, \N he’d go “Hey, you!”...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.27,0:02:38.73,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,...yelling with the {\i1}scariest{\i0} \N look on his face!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.73,0:02:40.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.06,0:02:41.85,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I can’t picture that at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:45.94,0:02:47.98,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,All right. Here you go!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.52,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,You’re a real pro, Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.69,0:02:56.23,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Now, now! Quiet down.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.60,0:03:00.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Todoggler really loves you, Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.23,0:03:03.60,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I actually met it{dread Todoggler} on my ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.60,0:03:06.23,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,It{dread Todoggler} was still \N just a Tamazarashi back then...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.94,0:03:12.10,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I was out at sea, fishing on my boat \N as usual, when suddenly...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:12.10,0:03:16.40,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,...a Tamazarashi that was swimming by \N hopped right onto my boat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.40,0:03:18.90,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I kept trying to put it{dread Todoggler} \N back in the sea,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.90,0:03:21.81,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,but every time I did, \N it{dread Todoggler} would leap back onto the boat.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.81,0:03:25.27,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Seemed to love being petted.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.27,0:03:29.60,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,It{dread Todoggler} grew real attached to me, \N and before I knew it, it{dread Todoggler} had won me over.{Implication being that Dan grew to love the ball BECAUSE of how clingy the ball was to him. -TLC}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.73,0:03:35.73,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,We’ve been joined at the hip ever since...{Literally he says they've been "running a three-legged race" but I think this gets the same point across while being easier to parse? https://jisho.org/search/%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%89%E8%84%9A -TLC}{Yeah this is a very good English equivalent. - Toa}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.73,0:03:39.65,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,...and then one day, it{dread Todoggler} finally evolved \N from Tamazarashi to Todoggler.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.90,0:03:43.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,You really must have worked hard, \N Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.44,0:03:45.27,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Good {going}stuff, Uncle!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.27,0:03:49.31,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I never thought \N it{dread Todoggler}’d grow {\i1}this{\i0} big, though.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.31,0:03:52.02,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,How’s Todoggler at home? \N You live in an apartment, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.44,0:03:54.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,You don’t live near the ocean?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.19,0:03:55.02,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:55.02,0:03:58.98,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, my son and his wife \N insisted I live near them.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.98,0:04:02.52,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I moved back when it{dread Todoggler} was still a Tamazarashi, \N and thought I could manage then...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.77,0:04:06.73,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,They’re not even close to \N the same size, after all.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.73,0:04:09.98,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Guess you keep it{dread Todoggler} in its{dread Todoggler} Monster Ball \N most of the time, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.02,0:04:19.02,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,About all I can do is let it{dread Todoggler} out \N at the nearby park every now and then.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.02,0:04:23.02,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,It’s been ages since it{dread Todoggler}’s been able to \N run and swim in such an open space,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:23.02,0:04:25.35,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,so it{dread Todoggler}’s really excited, y’know?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.31,0:04:30.85,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,But if it{dread Todoggler}’s causing trouble \N for all of you...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.85,0:04:32.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Don’t you worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.23,0:04:36.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,This is a place for Pokémon \N to have the time of their lives!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.85,Main,Guest,0,0,0,,See you soon!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:45.85,0:04:47.85,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,I brought snacks!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.85,0:04:55.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}! Ready when you are!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.81,0:05:06.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.06,0:05:20.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Todoggler really seems to be having a blast. \N Isn’t it{dread Todoggler} just adorable?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.56,0:05:21.60,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.60,0:05:25.65,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I haven’t seen Todoggler this happy \N in a very long time.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,How long have you been \N with Todoggler?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.48,0:05:32.06,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Fifteen years by now, I’d say.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:32.06,0:05:35.35,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,It{dread Todoggler} was so small \N back when it{dread Todoggler} was a Tamazarashi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.35,0:05:40.56,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,{\q2}It{dread Todoggler}’d waddle around on its{dread Todoggler} stumpy little legs \N and roll around like a ball whenever it{dread Todoggler} was in a good mood...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.56,0:05:44.60,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,It{dread Todoggler}’s given me... so much joy...
Comment: 10,0:05:51.35,0:05:51.35,Main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah, Mr. Tyler{Honorifics note: Tyler-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.52,0:06:07.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Good morning...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.23,0:06:10.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I see... I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:10.69,0:06:11.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.69,0:06:12.90,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:13.44,0:06:14.19,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.23,0:06:16.19,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:16.19,0:06:18.77,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Please keep looking \N over on your end as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:20.94,0:06:23.23,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Like we figured, \N he hasn’t gone back to his room.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.81,0:06:27.27,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,It seems there’s nobody in the salon \N who’s seen Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san} either.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.27,0:06:28.77,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,No, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.69,0:06:33.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Where could Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san} have gone \N that he’d leave Todoggler behind?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:33.44,0:06:36.15,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,You checked around the tents \N over here, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,He wasn’t here{as in, "in this location at which I am pointing"}, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.48,0:06:40.94,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Tyler, did you check by the river?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.90,0:06:42.73,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Tyler?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:42.73,0:06:44.02,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Oh... Right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.02,0:06:45.15,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.15,0:06:46.56,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.56,0:06:49.02,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,I’ll go check by the waterfall again.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.02,0:06:50.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’m coming with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.31,0:06:54.06,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,A-Ah... Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.27,0:07:05.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mr. Tyler{Honorifics note: Tyler-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.27,0:07:07.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,You don’t think Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san} might have...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.23,0:07:08.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,...gotten on the ship...?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.98,0:07:09.94,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.94,0:07:11.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It’s just about to set sail!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.27,0:07:13.35,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’ll go take a look!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.73,0:07:19.60,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah! There!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:22.69,0:07:24.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.69,0:07:33.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.06,0:07:34.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Todoggler?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.02,0:07:42.40,Main,PA,0,0,0,,{\an8}We have currently stopped for safety checks.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.40,0:07:45.77,Main,PA,0,0,0,,{\an8}We ask that you remain patient...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.77,Main,PA,0,0,0,,{\an8}...until we are able to proceed.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.40,0:07:44.65,Main,Guest,0,0,0,,Mommy! What’s the Todoggler{Honorifics note: Todoggler-san} doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.56,0:07:48.77,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Pardon... Excuse me.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.77,0:07:50.27,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Please let me through.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.77,0:07:59.31,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Todoggler! It’s dangerous here! \N Get away from the ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.77,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Go back to the port!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.81,0:08:07.73,Main,PA,0,0,0,,We will be temporarily returning \N to the Pokémon Resort.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.73,0:08:10.56,Main,PA,0,0,0,,We apologize for any delays \N to passengers in a hurry...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.90,0:08:14.40,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.31,0:08:20.40,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.98,0:08:22.15,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I’m so sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:22.81,0:08:24.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}... Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.90,0:08:26.15,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.15,0:08:29.23,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,You were attempting to \N abandon Todoggler here, were you not?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ms. Watanabe{Honorifics note: Watanabe-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.27,0:08:35.73,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,“Abandon”? Don’t say that...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.98,0:08:40.15,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0} is what leaving your Pokémon \N without permission is called.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.35,0:08:43.40,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,May I ask why?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.85,0:08:49.31,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Todoggler is a real rowdy Pokémon, \N as you can see...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.31,0:08:53.10,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,{I just thought}I felt it{dread Todoggler} was just getting to be \N too much for me to handle...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.10,0:08:57.27,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,You should have known from the beginning \N that Pokémon get bigger as they evolve.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.27,0:09:01.40,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,If you’re unwilling to stay with it{dread Todoggler} until the end, \N then you are not qualified to raise it{dread Todoggler}.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.02,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.15,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mr. Tyler{Honorifics note: Tyler-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.19,0:09:11.10,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Ms. Haru{Honorifics note: Haru-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:12.19,0:09:16.69,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}. Mr. Tyler{Honorifics note: Tyler-san} always talked about \N how strong and manly you were,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.69,0:09:18.85,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,and how proud he was \N to have you as his uncle.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.90,0:09:21.94,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,You were his hero, one could say.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.65,0:09:33.52,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Sorry for all the trouble \N I’ve caused you.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.35,0:09:39.15,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,You’ve always been \N crazy single-minded.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.77,0:09:42.81,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,You’d never go back on \N anything you set your mind to.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.02,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,That’s what I thought.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.85,0:09:47.85,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I can’t believe how pathetic I am.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.85,0:09:51.81,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Back when it{dread Todoggler} was still a Tamazarashi, \N things were manageable.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:51.81,0:09:57.31,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,{\q2}But then it{dread Todoggler} evolved into Todoggler, \N and suddenly I started worrying about the future.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.31,0:09:58.27,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,The future?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.81,0:10:01.77,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,It{dread Todoggler} will keep on growing.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.77,0:10:05.35,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Someday, it{dread Todoggler} might even \N become a Todoserga.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:05.85,0:10:10.10,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,And that’s why I thought \N living a laid-back life...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.10,0:10:13.27,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,...in a wide open place like this \N might make it{dread Todoggler} happier.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.60,0:10:16.31,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,That’s just a lame, easy excuse!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:16.31,0:10:17.27,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Tyler...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.27,0:10:22.27,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Back when I was a kid, didn’t you always say \N “No making excuses!”?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.27,0:10:27.77,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Uncle, are you really fine with \N parting ways with Todoggler?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.56,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I don’t want to leave it{dread Todoggler} either!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.56,0:10:37.31,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,But watching Todoggler yesterday made me think \Nthat it{dread Todoggler}’d be a lot happier living here...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.31,0:10:41.02,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,...instead of living \N in a tiny apartment with me.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.06,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.81,0:10:46.85,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,I know what to do, Uncle.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.23,0:10:47.85,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.85,0:10:50.27,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.27,0:10:53.27,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Let Todoggler stay here!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.85,0:10:55.06,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Tyler...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.77,0:10:58.35,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Please! I beg you!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.35,0:11:03.56,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Him trying to leave it{dread Todoggler} without permission \N was totally unacceptable,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:03.56,0:11:05.48,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,but Todoggler’s done \N nothing wrong!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.48,0:11:06.52,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.94,0:11:09.94,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Looking after Todoggler \N will be no easy task.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.94,0:11:12.60,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,I’ll take full responsibility for it{dread Todoggler}!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:12.60,0:11:14.35,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,You can’t.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:14.35,0:11:16.77,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,You’d be neglecting your work duties.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.77,0:11:19.73,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Please keep in mind \N that you are still a concierge.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:21.44,0:11:23.44,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,I’ll help, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:23.44,0:11:26.94,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,So please let Todoggler stay here.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.94,0:11:28.15,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Alisa...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:31.23,0:11:33.10,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,What do you think, Ms. Haru{Honorifics note: Haru-san}?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.10,0:11:35.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? Me?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I also...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.73,0:11:39.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,...plan to help out, of course...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:39.98,0:11:41.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:41.19,0:11:43.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’m not sure \N if that’s really for the best.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.15,0:11:45.02,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Haru...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.02,0:11:48.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Being separated from Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:48.23,0:11:53.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I have to wonder what will {\i1}actually{\i0} \N make Todoggler the happiest...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.27,0:11:55.73,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.73,0:11:58.19,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Only Todoggler \N knows the answer to that.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.77,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.77,0:12:08.10,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,We will look after Todoggler.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.10,0:12:12.06,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Todoggler seems to get along quite well \N with the other Pokémon.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.06,0:12:14.35,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I’m sure it{dread Todoggler} will liven up \N the island for everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.35,0:12:16.85,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.85,0:12:19.85,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,But I have one condition.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.85,0:12:22.56,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Yes! Whatever you ask.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.10,0:12:26.02,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Mr. Dan{Honorifics note: Dan-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.19,0:12:30.60,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Come work here.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:33.15,0:12:35.98,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,That way, you can stay \N with Todoggler, yes?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.19,0:12:38.73,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.73,0:12:42.60,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I could never, not after what I put \N all of you and Todoggler through...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:42.60,0:12:45.60,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,What you did was wrong.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.60,0:12:49.85,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,But it was a mistake made \N out of love for your Pokémon.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:50.27,0:12:54.73,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,I believe you can do good \N by the Pokémon who stay here.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.44,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Well done, Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.44,0:13:06.81,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,You’re great!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.81,0:13:13.77,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I’m sorry... \N I’m so sorry, Todoggler...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.31,0:13:22.27,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Ms. Watanabe{Honorifics note: Watanabe-san}... \N Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:22.27,0:13:23.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ms. Watanabe{Honorifics note: Watanabe-san}!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.73,0:13:27.02,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Ms. Watanabe{Honorifics note: Watanabe-san}, you’re the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:31.44,0:13:34.52,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,I look forward to \N working with you all!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.02,0:13:40.52,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,All right, Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.52,0:13:42.02,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Time to play!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:45.69,0:13:48.98,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Great, Todoggler! Keep it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,{\an8}Over here too, Todoggler!
Comment: 10,0:13:52.35,0:13:52.35,Main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:05.27,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}For so long, I’d been looking for you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.27,0:14:09.94,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(0,350)}And at last, I found you on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:15.94,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}What a beautiful sunset this is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:20.81,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I’m glad I got to see it with you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.81,0:14:23.69,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When I was alone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.69,0:14:26.40,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When I felt lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:31.10,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(0,350)}I would think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.77,0:14:37.02,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}Teach me, and only me
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:41.90,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Those secret onomatopoeia
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:46.85,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(0,350)}Let me hear even more of them
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:52.35,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}This is a healing island
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:55.02,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}A spark-sparkly island
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:15:00.27,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Overflowing with fluff-fluffy love
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:05.94,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Seeing you all shy, and just a bit embarrassed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:10.10,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I press my cheek against yours
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.10,0:15:11.69,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Time for a hug
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.69,0:15:12.90,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}(Time for a hug)
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:14.90,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(0,350)}Time to hold hands
